OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Pope is making a historic visit to 
OL,6, offer a formal apology on Canadian soil
OL,7, for the harms done by Catholic-run     
OL,8, residential schools across the country.
OL,10,FPope Francis, 85, has called the visit 
OL,11,Fa "pilgrimage of penance", and has said
OL,12,Fhe hopes it will help heal the wrongs  
OL,13,Fdone to indigenous people in Canada by 
OL,14,Fthe Roman Catholic Church.             
OL,16,FHis itinerary includes stops in the    
OL,17,Fprovinces of Alberta and Quebec and the
OL,18,Fnorthern territory of Nunavut.         
